{"tid":1006692,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 特 製 利 是 封：個 利 是 封 有 我 個 樣  有 收 藏 價 值","createTime":"2019-02-03T07:31:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T10:11:35.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7f50bcc568ee6e001b2cd069f2ba44c835c20c7","tid":1006692,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:31:10.000Z","msg":"「個利是封有我個樣，是特別去整的」<br />\n<br />\n吳業坤到灣仔出席年宵活動，他表示明日開完工就收爐放假，至初七才開工，笑言年三十晚會去行年宵執平貨，問到和誰去？他說：「一個人，順道去識新朋友，也會買桃花。」又說已準備好利是，但事先講明叫大家不要介意內涵，「個利是封有我個樣，是特別去整的，成本都貴，有收藏價值，初七開工會出席電影《你咪理，我愛你！》慶功，好多前輩出席，會主動去講恭喜發財逗行利是，希望賺賺外快，cover派出去的利是錢。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/01/20190131_EN_%E5%90%B3%E6%A5%AD%E5%9D%A4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F01%2F20190131_EN_%25E5%2590%25B3%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%259D%25A4.jpg&h=d16c44d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"560320ae53944a8400b187f9daa4b5ed3868e9e7","tid":1006692,"uid":121911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:32:34.000Z","msg":"下半身老女人著法<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2c2ed29525fd5ea31fd0cf32382d72ff2c1f63","tid":1006692,"uid":132587,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T07:33:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20180205/_2018020512174738161.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20180205%2F_2018020512174738161.jpg&h=0b00a210&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d5e421cc1f8bc916808619bffd3c27ceae649979","tid":1006692,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T10:11:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}